{"word":"μόλις","slug":"μόλις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μόλις</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>later form for <a href='S:μόγις'><el>μόγις</el></a>, <b><a href='S:Tragic, in Tragic Greek'>Trag.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>\n<p/>with a <a href='S:negativum'>negat.</a>, <el>οὐ μόλις</el> <i>not scarcely</i>, <a href='S:id est'>i. e.</a> <i>quite, utterly</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/>"}]}